OL,5,G1515 Motorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,6,G     Speeders
OL,7,     FNorthumbria Police face a daily
OL,8,     Fbattle with dangerous and illegal
OL,9,     Fmotorbike use. In Newcastle, cops
OL,10,     Fpursue - by car and chopper - a
OL,11,     Fgroup riding off-road.
OL,12,G1615 Motorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,13,G     Speeders
OL,14,     FA driver seems more concerned
OL,15,     Fabout losing his footwear than
OL,16,     Fgetting nicked! And late night, a
OL,17,     FPC hunts for a suspected cloned
OL,18,     Fcar linked to a recent burglary.
